acceptance_criteria: Duplicate-safe status-all lineage search is recorded; all open capability epics are inspected; missing backlog is added under canonical parents; tracker health and validation pass; repo gates pass; PR review agents report no remaining findings; GitHub checks are green; Sentry and telemetry freshness are verified.
