goal: project management = context management
objective: "Normalize the pm-cli tracker so features, code, tests, docs, goals, issues, decisions, epics, user stories, tasks, chores, improvements, and observability follow-up are represented as non-duplicated pm items."
value: "A clean, non-duplicated tracker gives humans and agents a reliable context graph for the entire pm ecosystem."
why_now: "The user requested a detailed manual inspection of all pm items and a best-practice organization pass before PR, review, merge, Sentry, and telemetry closeout."
