close_reason: "PM ecosystem audit, backlog normalization, reliability fixes, local gates, PR checks, and available AI review loop completed."
body: "Scope: inspect the current pm-cli tracker as a living context map, verify the capability epic taxonomy, add or refine only non-duplicated actionable items, and record evidence through pm comments/files/tests/docs. Philosophy: project management = context management. Boundaries: use pm CLI mutations only; keep public docs free of private runbook details; do not hand-edit .agents/pm files."
